}$ and IRT \textit{bla}$_{\text{TEM}}$ genes were found among the AMP$^{\text{r}}$ E. coli isolates from foods and the feces of humans and healthy animals, and a new gene, \textit{bla}$_{\text{TEM-95b}}$ (P3), was detected.},
